            I've been making games for fun and for research. For example, I
            built a couple simple video games for stroke survivors.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <TranslateButton />

    <section class="projects-section" id="collapsible_section_1">
      <h2 data-translation="Projets">Projects</h2>

      <div class="spaced-group">
