            <h4 data-translation="Ce que j'ai fait :">What I did:</h4>
            <p>
              <span
                data-translation="J'ai contribué plus de 8 PR (Pull Requests), y compris"
                >I contributed over 8 PRs (Pull Requests), including</span
              >
              <a
