            <h4 data-translation="Comment :">How:</h4>
            <p>
              <span data-translation="J'ai créé mon propre">Created my own</span
              >
              <a
                href="https://github.com/hchiam/_2DNote/pkgs/npm/2dnote"
                target="_blank"
                data-translation="package npm 2dnote,">npm package 2dnote,</a
